you can see them.

00:02:46.620 --> 00:02:47.940 align:middle line:90%
You can differentiate.

00:02:47.940 --> 00:02:50.790 align:middle line:84%
Yes, this was the
single first cause.

00:02:50.790 --> 00:02:53.700 align:middle line:84%
