every 300 years.

00:35:19.260 --> 00:35:21.680 align:middle line:84%
And when these layers
are in alignment,

00:35:21.680 --> 00:35:23.300 align:middle line:84%
meaning less and
less disturbance,

00:35:23.300 --> 00:35:26.120 align:middle line:84%
less and less energy coming
off, less and less agitation

00:35:26.120 --> 00:35:29.390 align:middle line:84%
