00:38:10.190 --> 00:38:12.110 align:middle line:10%
for three centuries.

00:38:12.110 --> 00:38:16.130 align:middle line:10%
Professor Valentina Zharkova of
the University of Northumbria

00:38:16.130 --> 00:38:18.680 align:middle line:10%
presented the findings
at the National Astronomy

00:38:18.680 --> 00:38:21.680 align:middle line:10%
Meeting in Wales this week,
Britain's "Independent"

00:38:21.680 --> 00:38:23.640 align:middle line:10%
