The last time the Earth was hit
by such alarming solar activity

00:38:40.220 --> 00:38:43.770 align:middle line:10%
happened 300 years ago
during the Maunder minimum,

00:38:43.770 --> 00:38:47.990 align:middle line:10%
which lasted from 1645 to 1715.

00:38:47.990 --> 00:38:50.600 align:middle line:10%
Scientists say there are
magnetic waves in the sun's

00:38:50.600 --> 00:38:53.030 align:middle line:10%
interior that fluctuate
between the body's

00:38:53.030 --> 00:38:54.980 align:middle line:10%
northern and
southern hemispheres,

00:38:54.980 --> 00:38:58.280 align:middle line:10%
resulting in various solar
conditions over a period of 10

00:38:58.280 --> 00:38:59.990 align:middle line:10%
